---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="BeaconGuard Architecture">
  <section>
    <h1>System Architecture</h1>

    <p>
      BeaconGuard is composed of a policy control plane, a deterministic
      enforcement runtime, and an append-only audit ledger.
    </p>

    <figure>
      <img
        src="/diagrams/beaconguard-architecture.svg"
        alt="BeaconGuard Assurance architecture diagram"
        style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"
      />
      <figcaption>
        High-level component boundaries and trust domains.
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

  <center>  <p>
      The diagram illustrates static structural relationships only.
      It does not imply execution order or runtime flow.
    </p> </center>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>